h3. Problem Definition
The JIRA Latest REST API documentation is not showing the actual latest documentation. That is, this URL:
{panel}
https://docs.atlassian.com/jira/REST/latest/
{panel}
Shows the REST documentation for JIRA 6.4.12 instead of JIRA 7.0.

h3. Suggested Solution
Update the redirection so this URL shows the JIRA 7.0.0 REST API documentation instead.

h3. Workaround 
Access the JIRA 7.0.0 documentation directly through:
{panel}
https://docs.atlassian.com/jira/REST/7.0.0/
{panel}
